The,Lookup,Country,Information,API,simplifies,the,search,for,country,profiles,using,letters,or,numeric,ISO,country,codes,The,use,of,two,letter,and,three,letter,codes,or,numeric,codes,is,sufficient,to,generate,descriptive,details,of,a,country,including,its,name,and,continent,as,well,as,its,associated,alpha,or,numeric,ISO,codes,The,API,sends,requests,in,URI,Query,String,CRUD,format,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format